A Scottish comedian's tweet has gone viral after he created a new schoolbag for his daughter - out of a 12 pack of beer.Funnyman Joe Heenan tweeted out, &quot;My daughter couldn't find her school bag this morning so I made her one.&quot;Immediately the tweet went viral with Capital Scotland breakfast host Des McLean and Jennie Cook sharing it on their social media and talking about the quirky accessory on their morning show.&nbsp;And it seems the unusual bag got the seal of approval from Twitter:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;